Then we have 2025+2027+2070+2071+2072+2073+2074+2075 = 16387

Let N be the number in the center.
The sum of the neighbors is $8N$. If $N=1$, then 8.
Let the neighbors of 2026 be $x_1, x_2, \dots, x_8$. We want $\sum_{i=1}^8 x_i$.
$2026(8) = 16208$, close to our 16387.

